Maintainer: Paul Bovbel <paul@bovbel.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), ros-melodic-catkin, ros-melodic-message-filters, ros-melodic-nodelet, ros-melodic-roscpp, ros-melodic-roslint, ros-melodic-sensor-msgs, ros-melodic-tf2, ros-melodic-tf2-ros, ros-melodic-tf2-sensor-msgs
Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/perception_pcl
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-melodic-pointcloud-to-laserscan
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-melodic-message-filters, ros-melodic-nodelet, ros-melodic-roscpp, ros-melodic-sensor-msgs, ros-melodic-tf2, ros-melodic-tf2-ros, ros-melodic-tf2-sensor-msgs
Description: Converts a 3D Point Cloud into a 2D laser scan.
 This is useful for making devices like the Kinect appear like a laser scanner for 2D-based algorithms (e.g. laser-based SLAM).
